>
	<Header />
	<main>
		<section class="seo-hero section">
			<div class="container">
				<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="breadcrumb">
					<ol>
						<li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
						<li>Search Engine Optimization</li>
					</ol>
				</nav>
				<div class="hero-content">
					<p class="eyebrow">Organic Search Engine Optimization</p>
					<h1>SEO That Pairs Technical Precision with Real Content Strategy</h1>
					<p class="hero-subtitle">
						InfraDev manages every part of your SEO program—from focus keywords and bilingual content to technical fixes, analytics, and monthly reporting—so your site earns sustainable rankings and trust.
					</p>
					<div class="hero-cta">
						<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book an SEO Consultation</a>
						<a href={brochureUrl} class="btn btn-secondary" download>Download SEO Brochure</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="overview section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>What You Get with InfraDev SEO</h2>
					<p>We blend strategy, copywriting, development, and analytics to ensure search engines—and your customers—experience the same high-quality website.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="overview-grid">
					<div class="overview-card">
						<h3>Keyword & Content Control</h3>
						<p>Focus keyword planning (kept between 2–3% density), professional copywriting, AI-text refinement, and French localization keep every page aligned with your brand.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="overview-card">
						<h3>Technical Site Health</h3>
						<p>Broken link removal, redirection clean-up, image compression, metadata, and mobile-first improvements keep crawlers and users confident.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="overview-card">
						<h3>Performance Benchmarks</h3>
						<p>Critical error remediation plus ongoing Core Web Vitals work to keep load times around two seconds on desktop and mobile.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="overview-card">
						<h3>Transparent Reporting</h3>
						<p>Google Analytics setup, KPI dashboards, backlink tracking, and monthly summaries (with optional mid-month check-ins).</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="resource-link-box">
					<p><strong>Learn more about search optimization:</strong> <a href="/resources/what-is-aeo">What is AEO?</a> | <a href="/resources/what-is-geo">What is GEO?</a> | <a href="/resources/seo-aeo-geo-complete-strategy">SEO vs AEO vs GEO Complete Strategy</a></p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="services section" id="seo-services">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>SEO Services Included</h2>
					<p>Everything below is managed by InfraDev unless noted otherwise.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="services-grid">
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Business_blue.svg" alt="Organic Optimization" />
						</div>
						<h3>Organic Optimization</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Manage focus keywords with 2–3% density</li>
							<li>Dedicated content writer and editor</li>
							<li>Upgrade on-page copy to match focus topics</li>
							<li>Reduce AI-generated text for authenticity</li>
							<li>Adapt messaging for French-language audiences</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Software_dualtone.png" alt="Technical SEO & UX" />
						</div>
						<h3>Technical SEO & UX</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Fix broken links, remove low-quality backlinks</li>
							<li>Resolve critical site errors & simplify redirects</li>
							<li>Image optimization and compression</li>
							<li>Meta titles, descriptions, Open Graph tags</li>
							<li>Sitemap & robots.txt management</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/build.png" alt="Performance & Mobile" />
						</div>
						<h3>Performance & Mobile</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Site speed review with ~2 second target</li>
							<li>Mobile friendliness improvements</li>
							<li>Core Web Vitals & UX enhancements</li>
							<li>Hosting/caching recommendations</li>
							<li>Accessibility best practices</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Quality_blue.svg" alt="Content & Authority" />
						</div>
						<h3>Content & Authority</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Two new blogs created every month</li>
							<li>Optional reputable backlinks ($70 USD/link)</li>
							<li>Editorial calendar & brief creation</li>
							<li>Internal linking and CTA optimization</li>
							<li>Focus keyword tracking per post</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<div class="service-icon">
							<img src="/assets/WebsiteMarketing/InfraDev Assets/Estimate_recolored.png" alt="Analytics & Reporting" />
						</div>
						<h3>Analytics & Reporting</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Google Analytics & Search Console setup</li>
							<li>Open Graph protocol validation</li>
							<li>Monthly progress report (mid-month update if needed)</li>
							<li>Goal alignment and KPI dashboards</li>
							<li>Clear next-step recommendations</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="workflow section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>How Our SEO Engagement Works</h2>
					<p>Clear milestones keep your internal team aligned with every optimization task.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="workflow-steps">
					<div class="workflow-step">
						<h3>1. Audit & Roadmap</h3>
						<p>Full crawl, keyword mapping, and prioritization of technical fixes with projected impact.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="workflow-step">
						<h3>2. Content & Technical Sprint</h3>
						<p>Writers and engineers execute copy updates, new blogs, link clean-up, and speed improvements.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="workflow-step">
						<h3>3. Measurement & Reporting</h3>
						<p>Google Analytics dashboards, backlink tracking, and monthly summaries delivered to stakeholders.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="brochure-download">
					<p>Prefer a one-pager overview? Download the brochure anytime.</p>
					<a href={brochureUrl} class="btn btn-secondary" download>Download SEO Brochure</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Pricing Section -->
		<section class="pricing section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Transparent Pricing</h2>
					<p>Simple, straightforward pricing with no hidden fees</p>
				</div>
				<div class="pricing-content">
					<div class="pricing-card">
						<h3>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</h3>
						<div class="pricing-amount">
							<GeoPricing usdPrice={899} cadPrice={1099} showCurrencyToggle={false} />
						</div>
						<div class="bundle-offer">
							<h4>Complete Search Optimization Bundle</h4>
							<p>Get all three services SEO + AEO + GEO for maximum visibility:</p>
							<div class="bundle-price">
								<GeoPricing usdPrice={2499} cadPrice={2999} showCurrencyToggle={false} />
							</div>
							<p class="bundle-savings">Save <span class="geo-percentage-inline" data-usd-percent="8" data-cad-percent="10">8%</span> compared to individual services</p>
							<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Complete Bundle</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="faq section" id="faq">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
					<p>Common questions about our SEO services</p>
				</div>
				<div class="faq-list">
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-1">
							<span>How long does it take to see SEO results?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-1">
							<p>SEO is a long-term strategy. Typically, you'll start seeing improvements in 3-6 months, with significant results appearing after 6-12 months of consistent optimization. Technical fixes and site speed improvements may show results sooner, while keyword rankings and organic traffic growth take longer to develop.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-2">
							<span>What's included in your SEO service?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-2">
							<p>Our SEO service includes keyword research and management, professional content writing (including French localization), technical SEO fixes, site speed optimization, mobile optimization, Google Analytics setup, monthly blog creation (2 posts per month), backlink building (optional at $70/link), and comprehensive monthly reporting with KPI dashboards.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-3">
							<span>Do you work with existing content or create new content?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-3">
							<p>We do both. We'll optimize your existing pages for focus keywords and improve on-page SEO elements. Additionally, we create two new blog posts every month as part of our content strategy to build authority and target long-tail keywords.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">
							<span>What is keyword density and why is it important?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-4">
							<p>Keyword density refers to how often a focus keyword appears on a page relative to the total word count. We maintain a 2-3% keyword density to ensure your content is optimized for search engines without appearing spammy. This helps search engines understand what your page is about while maintaining natural, readable content.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-5">
							<span>How do you handle bilingual content (English and French)?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-5">
							<p>We have dedicated content writers who can create and optimize content in both English and French. This is particularly valuable for Canadian markets or businesses serving bilingual audiences. We ensure proper localization, not just translation, to maintain SEO effectiveness in both languages.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-6">
							<span>What technical SEO issues do you fix?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-6">
							<p>We address broken links, remove low-quality backlinks, fix critical site errors, simplify redirect chains, optimize images, implement proper meta tags and Open Graph tags, manage sitemaps and robots.txt files, and improve Core Web Vitals for better site performance.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7">
							<span>How do you measure SEO success?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7">
							<p>We track multiple KPIs including organic traffic growth, keyword rankings, backlink quality and quantity, site speed metrics (targeting ~2 seconds load time), Core Web Vitals scores, conversion rates, and goal completions. You'll receive monthly reports with clear metrics and recommendations.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-8">
							<span>Can I see examples of your SEO work?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-8">
							<p>Yes, we can provide case studies and examples of SEO improvements we've achieved for clients. Contact us to discuss your specific needs and see how we've helped similar businesses improve their organic visibility and rankings.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-9">
							<span>What's the difference between SEO and paid advertising?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-9">
							<p>SEO focuses on earning organic (free) search rankings through content optimization, technical improvements, and authority building. Paid advertising (PPC) involves paying for immediate visibility in search results. SEO provides long-term, sustainable results, while PPC offers immediate but temporary visibility. Many businesses use both strategies together.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="faq-item">
						<button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-10">
							<span>Do you provide monthly reports?</span>
							<span class="faq-icon">+</span>
						</button>
						<div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-10">
							<p>Yes, we provide comprehensive monthly reports that include keyword rankings, traffic analytics, backlink tracking, technical health metrics, and clear recommendations for next steps. We also offer optional mid-month check-ins if you need more frequent updates.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Related Services Section -->
		<section class="related-services section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>Complete Your Search Strategy</h2>
					<p>SEO is just one part of modern search optimization. Combine it with AEO and GEO for maximum visibility</p>
				</div>
				<div class="related-grid">
					<a href="/aeo" class="related-card">
						<h3>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</h3>
						<p>Optimize for AI-powered answer engines like Google AI Overviews, Perplexity, and voice assistants that provide direct answers.</p>
						<span class="related-link">Learn about AEO →</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/geo" class="related-card">
						<h3>Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</h3>
						<p>Optimize for ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, and other generative AI systems that create new content based on web sources.</p>
						<span class="related-link">Learn about GEO →</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/resources/seo-aeo-geo-complete-strategy" class="related-card">
						<h3>Complete Strategy Guide</h3>
						<p>Learn how SEO, AEO, and GEO work together for comprehensive search visibility across all platforms.</p>
						<span class="related-link">Read the guide →</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Case Studies & Portfolio Section -->
		<section class="related-work section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="section-header">
					<h2>See Our SEO Work</h2>
					<p>Explore case studies and portfolio examples of our search optimization services</p>
				</div>
				<div class="related-grid">
					<a href="/case-study" class="related-card">
						<h3>Case Studies</h3>
						<p>Real results from real clients. See how we've helped businesses achieve growth through SEO, AEO, and GEO optimization.</p>
						<span class="related-link">View case studies →</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/portfolio" class="related-card">
						<h3>Portfolio</h3>
						<p>Explore websites we've built and continue to service with ongoing SEO, AEO, and GEO optimization.</p>
						<span class="related-link">View portfolio →</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="cta section">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cta-content">
					<h2>Ready to Transform Your Organic Visibility?</h2>
					<p>Let's turn your site into the fastest, cleanest, bilingual experience in your industry.</p>
					<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-cta">Schedule a Call</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>

